00:04:24,939 --> 00:04:26,982
Dekontaminasi selesai.

32
00:04:44,872 --> 00:04:46,623
- Richard.
- Richard!

33
00:04:46,706 --> 00:04:51,293
Richard.

34
00:04:51,377 --> 00:04:52,670
Richard.

35
00:04:56,589 --> 00:04:59,592
Bagaimana kau
akan menyelesaikan yang itu?

36
00:05:09,141 --> 00:05:10,183
Bagus.

37
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:17,981
Tidur yang nyenyak, Christopher.

38
