Kurang 15 detik. Peluncuran siap
dalam 13, 12, 11...

64
00:06:45,884 --> 00:06:48,261
Beralih dari GLC ke OBC.

65
00:06:49,262 --> 00:06:51,347
Enam, lima...

66
00:06:51,556 --> 00:06:53,224
Nyalakan mesin utama.

67
00:06:53,307 --> 00:06:56,643
Tiga, dua, satu...

68
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:42,763
Hai.

69
